author: maxb
msg: mod_dav_svn: A collection of tidying centered around repos.c, which led to
discovering that dav_svn_resource_kind() is dead code.
* dav_svn.h: Collect repos.c functions together in single section.
* repos.c: Throughout, remove dav_svn_ and svn_dav__ namespacing prefixes
from static functions and locally-defined types.
Move private structure definitions to immediately before their first use.
(dav_svn_resource_kind): Rename to resource_kind, and surround in "#if 0",

author: maxb
msg: mod_dav_svn: Unravel a small piece of unnecessary indirection.
dav_svn_register_uris() at this, its only call site.
* liveprops.c (dav_svn_liveprop_group): Define later, so that a forward
declaration of dav_svn_hooks_liveprop is not needed.

author: maxb
msg: mod_dav_svn: Fork the remaining REPORT implementations which were embedded

Remove doc-comment for file-revs-report to the .c file, for parity with
* version.c: Remove the inline report implementations.
